item.title: The single became a Top 40 hit on both the Billboard Hot 100 and in the UK, peaking at #15 and #26. It earned a Platinum certification in the US.

item.title: The fourth single off ‘1989’ became the third #1 hit off the album on the Billboard Hot 100 and broke the 24-hour VEVO record at the time. It won Video Of The Year at the VMAs and a Grammy for Best Video.
